## GSAP CORE RULES

- Use GSAP for all advanced animations (no CSS hacks for complex motion)
- Always use gsap.context() in React/Next.js
- Always clean up animations to prevent memory leaks

Example pattern:

```js
useEffect(() => {
  const ctx = gsap.context(() => {
    // animations here
  });

  return () => ctx.revert();
}, []);
```
